archimate:Requirement.name: SY.1.1.10d: d) permitting only execute (i.e. not read or write) access to executable software (e.g. run-time code, stored procedures and Common Gateway Interface (CGI) scripts).
archimate:Requirement.documentation: This is a standard topic modelled from the 2022 Version of the Standards Of Good Practice by ISF. It has been adopted as version 3 of the Security Baseline.
